org.apache.james.mailbox.store.mail

Interface MailboxMapper<Id>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Mapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HBaseMailboxMapper, InMemoryMailboxMapper, JCRMailboxMapper, JPAMailboxMapper, MaildirMailboxMapper

    public interface MailboxMapper<Id>
extends Mapper
    Mapper for Mailbox actions. A MailboxMapper has a lifecycle from the start of a request to the end of the request.
